I'm Rula Tamimi. I'm a cancer epidemiologist, and I'm at Weill

6
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.900
Cornell Medicine in New York City.

7
00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:27.340
So in terms of our format, I'm just going to give five minutes of intro to

8
